1
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:45,000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:51,880
I am telling you

3
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:55,240
the secret I wanted to seal away forever.

4
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,600
Can you…

5
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,720
Can you believe

6
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,320
that you are a great person?

7
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,919
Seeing how much

8
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,240
I like you,

9
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:16,800
can you ignore what people say about you?

10
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,640
Can you be with me forever?

11
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:30,160
MAKE A LOT OF MONEY
AND HELP HIM PAY OFF HIS DEBTS

12
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:34,920
Please?

13
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,560
How do you fold this star?

14
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,000
I can't fold it back after unfolding it.

15
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,360
After unfolding it, I…

16
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,640
These stars

17
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,920
will be in my safekeeping.

18
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,960
What should I do now?

19
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,040
Counting it now,

20
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,000
I've made you cry so many times.

21
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,800
Yet you deny that you're a crybaby.

22
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,360
Give me a hug.

23
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,280
All right.

24
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,640
I know it all now.

25
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,200
Why did you suddenly tell me this?

26
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,279
I just wanted you to know.

27
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,959
But this time,

28
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,280
I don't have that rumored girlfriend

29
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,480
that your brother mentioned.

30
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:27,280
I have an official girlfriend now.

31
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:33,920
So did you come back to Yihe

32
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,200
just to tell me this?

33
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,200
It's because you said

34
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,600
you were considering something.

35
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,920
That's why…

36
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,720
I was afraid that if I called you,
you would…

37
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,520
I thought that
if I talked to you in person,

38
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:58,560
it should be hard for you to bring it up.

39
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,560
Bring what up?

40
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,280
What were you thinking?

41
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,960
If your parents hadn't disapproved,

42
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:19,160
I would snatch you
to get our marriage certificate now.

43
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,920
I'm serious.

44
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:25,360
Why would you have to snatch me?

45
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:28,080
I'm afraid you will run away.

46
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,320
When I said I was considering something,

47
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:35,000
it was whether I should stay with you
in Yihe for two years

48
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,160
and go back with you after you graduate

49
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,800
or if I should go to Nanwu first

50
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,880
to get everything settled

51
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:41,000
and wait for you to return.

52
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,280
What were you thinking?

53
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,720
Is that it?

54
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,840
Actually,

55
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,680
I could stay in Yihe too.

56
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,040
We can talk about it.

57
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,800
You don't always have to give in to me.

58
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,160
I really don't want to stay here.

59
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,880
Besides, who else would I give in to?

60
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,880
Young lady,

61
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:15,240
what you need to do is simple.

62
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,280
Stay here and study hard.

63
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,640
Don't worry about anything else.

64
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,000
The most important thing

65
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,400
is to spend more time with your boyfriend.

66
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,760
Understand?

67
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,320
As for your parents,

68
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,000
don't worry about it.

69
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,400
I'll find time to talk to them.

70
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,280
Smile.

71
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,160
Give me a smile.

72
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:14,400
CHAPTER 24, SET OFF

73
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,560
SO NEAR AND YET SO FAR

74
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:36,520
There is someone

75
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,880
that I really like.

76
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,480
But

77
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,240
he just doesn't like me.

78
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,280
But I will grow up.

79
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,440
Then let's wait until you grow up.

80
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,440
But when I grow up,

81
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,160
he'll fall for someone else.

82
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,080
That's fine.

83
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,760
Sang Zhi, when you grow up,

84
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,400
you will meet someone better.

85
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,320
Why have you been drinking?

86
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,320
What's wrong?

87
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,120
I'll bring you some hot water.

88
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,440
Why did you get up?

89
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,840
Are you in a bad mood?

90
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,800
I think

91
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,360
that I've treated you badly.

92
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,520
When did you treat me badly?

93
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,360
Is it because of what I said to you

94
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,840
at the airport today?

95
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,560
I told you that

96
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:38,360
because I just wanted you to know.

97
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,800
You didn't know it before.

98
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,440
That's why I wanted to tell you.

99
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:44,320
But I didn't want you to feel…

100
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:53,160
You treat me very well.

101
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,840
Be it in the past or the present,

102
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,160
you treat me well.

103
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:00,520
It's true.

104
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,480
Sang Zhi.

105
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,440
I love you.

106
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,520
I'm sorry, Zhizhi.

107
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,560
I said these words so late.

108
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,640
Over the years,

109
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,960
I know

110
00:10:35,280 --> 00:10:36,440
I've made you sad.

111
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,120
It was your unwavering dedication

112
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:46,080
that made me realize I'm not good enough.

113
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,440
Whether it's my imperceptiveness

114
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,400
or indecisiveness,

115
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:56,240
I haven't been good enough.

116
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,200
But for these shortcomings,

117
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,840
I'll try my best to make it up to you

118
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,200
every day that we are together.

119
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,200
Zhizhi.

120
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,600
I won't let you regret

121
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,640
the choice you made.

122
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,920
I love you, Sang Zhi.

123
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,120
Sangsang, what are you drawing?

124
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:51,160
I found my theme for the competition.

125
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,640
What did I tell you?

126
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,920
You can't force ideas to come.

127
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,160
You need to clear your mind

128
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,560
for inspiration to come.

129
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,920
So what is your theme?

130
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,880
Why are you being secretive?

131
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,240
Come in.

132
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,200
Siyun.

133
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:23,200
Perfect timing. Come here quickly.

134
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,440
Help me take a look.

135
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,000
I have trouble deciding.

136
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,480
Which one of these two is better?

137
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,840
I think

138
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:31,360
this one is the best.

139
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,160
-What is this?
-Open it.

140
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:37,080
You've been working late nights lately,

141
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,280
so I bought you a gift.

142
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,760
Restorative honey?

143
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:42,840
Xiaoduan recommended it.

144
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:46,680
He sure knows what to pick.

145
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:48,280
This kid knows a lot of things.

146
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,400
It smells quite nice.

147
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,600
Come in.

148
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,120
Actually, I wanted to talk

149
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:00,120
to both of you about something today.

150
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,000
What is it?

151
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,160
I was thinking

152
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,800
that after completing the upgrade

153
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,360
of the Celestial Progression System,

154
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,840
I might have to resign.

155
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,160
Resign?

156
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,920
Why do you suddenly want to resign?

157
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,280
Is another company trying to poach you?

158
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:19,440
No.

159
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,640
I'm thinking of going back to Nanwu

160
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,000
to start my own business.

161
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:24,400
Nanwu?

162
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,680
Is it for Sang Zhi?

163
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,800
If I'm not mistaken,

164
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,360
isn't she only a college sophomore?

165
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,320
When she graduates in two years,

166
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,480
you can still go back there with her.

167
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,040
The Dream Games studio

168
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:41,480
has a very promising next few years.

169
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,920
Are you sure about leaving now?

170
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:48,000
I have carefully considered it

171
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,360
before telling you.

172
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:53,640
Some things have happened recently.

173
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,280
It made me realize

174
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:57,160
I may not have been good enough

175
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,640
to Sang Zhi.

176
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:00,280
I haven't done enough for her either.

177
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,920
No, Jiaxu, you're worrying too much.

178
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,280
Siyun and I both think
that you treat her really well.

179
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,600
Actually, the main reason

180
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,760
is that her parents

181
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:12,520
may have some concerns about me.

182
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:18,280
Sang Zhi is also upset

183
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:19,840
because of this.

184
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,480
However,

185
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,480
she turned around and comforted me.

186
00:15:25,520 --> 00:15:26,960
She was worried

187
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,560
that this might hurt my self-esteem.

188
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,080
In truth, I understand

189
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:31,600
her parents' concerns.

190
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,640
But I'm older than her.

191
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,840
So I should be the one

192
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,360
resolving these concerns.

193
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:40,720
I just want to go

194
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,440
to Nanwu as soon as possible.

195
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:44,520
After I've settled everything,

196
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:47,000
I'll give myself more time

197
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,760
and chances to prove myself.

198
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,800
He's all grown up now.

199
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:56,160
A man should have
a sense of responsibility.

200
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:04,360
Since you've already made up your mind,

201
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:06,880
Li Xun and I can't stop you.

202
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,120
We wish you all the best.

203
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,320
Thank you.

204
00:16:12,400 --> 00:16:13,240
However,

205
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:16,960
today's economy isn't easy

206
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,040
for young entrepreneurs.

207
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:20,360
Given your qualifications,

208
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:22,200
there aren't many
reputable companies in Nanwu

209
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,160
that can hire you.

210
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,320
How about this?

211
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,760
You can apply to our headquarters

212
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,640
to open your own studio.

213
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:31,520
They can provide some technical support

214
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,920
and follow-up expansion,

215
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,880
which would be relatively easier for you.

216
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:35,920
Look at that.

217
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,600
Siyun thinks of everything.

218
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,160
Our company does have this policy.

219
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:41,120
If you need it,
Siyun and I will put in a word.

220
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,600
It would be great if that could happen.

221
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,120
Thank you, Li Xun.

222
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:48,040
Thank you, Siyun.

223
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,080
You're welcome.

224
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:53,040
If you create a successful game
in the future,

225
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,360
I'll get to boast about it.

226
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:56,080
I can say that I mentored this guy.

227
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,120
You were still an intern

228
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,800
when you first came.

229
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:02,720
Look at you now.

230
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,720
So many years have passed.

231
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:07,040
Now that you're leaving,

232
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:08,560
I'm actually quite reluctant.

233
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,240
You can do it.

234
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:14,240
-Good luck.
-LI Xun and I support you.

235
00:17:14,319 --> 00:17:15,560
-You can do it.
-I'll do my best.

236
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,320
Hello?

237
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:38,240
The patient's condition isn't optimistic.

238
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,240
Cherish the time and talk to him.

239
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:41,920
Thank you, doctor.

240
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:31,880
It has been a long time
since I thought about the past.

241
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,240
I didn't want to

242
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,880
and I didn't dare to.

243
00:18:41,280 --> 00:18:42,280
But I think

244
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:45,280
today should be the day that I face it.

245
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,920
I should get some closure.

246
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,040
It happened such a long time ago.

247
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,960
Now that I think about it,

248
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:01,200
you would have been released by now

249
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,920
if you hadn't jumped.

250
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,480
There are many things

251
00:19:12,040 --> 00:19:13,560
that I've never told you.

252
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:19,120
I've finished paying off

253
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:22,360
the compensation you owed

254
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,680
and those debts of yours.

255
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:28,200
My mom

256
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,360
passed away several years ago.

257
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,280
Because of you.

258
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,480
Because we didn't have money.

259
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:54,200
At that time,

260
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,520
she knew she was sick

261
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,600
from cancer.

262
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:02,040
She refused to get treatment

263
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,640
because she didn't want to spend money.

264
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:09,440
When she finally went to the hospital,

265
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,920
the doctor said
it was too late for treatment.

266
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:28,120
I used to wish so badly
that you could see it all.

267
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:31,520
I wished you would wake up,

268
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:35,840
so you could see everything
that happened to us.

269
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,480
I wanted to see you feel guilt and pain.

270
00:20:45,640 --> 00:20:47,640
I just wanted you to understand.

271
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:51,040
If you hadn't

272
00:20:52,360 --> 00:20:53,600
run away

273
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,920
and had chosen to face punishment,

274
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,880
our lives would have been so different.

275
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:16,080
But actually,

276
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,400
I should thank you too.

277
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:22,960
Because of you,

278
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:25,560
I never dared to drink.

279
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,840
It was also because of you

280
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:31,200
that I learned what responsibility

281
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,640
and taking on responsibility means.

282
00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:36,160
Now,

283
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:42,480
I can say

284
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,040
that I'm a decent person.

285
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:49,480
At least I now have the ability

286
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,920
to protect the people I love.

287
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:56,640
I really wish you could see it.

288
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:06,760
All right then.

289
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,160
If you see Mom

290
00:22:13,120 --> 00:22:14,520
on the other side,

291
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:19,640
sincerely apologize to her.

292
00:22:30,520 --> 00:22:31,480
Be at peace,

293
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,200
Dad.

294
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:54,880
Why are you here?

295
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,480
What's with this expression?

296
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:03,800
I knew

297
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:05,840
this day would come eventually.

298
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,440
I know.

299
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,600
I know you're very sad.

300
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:52,840
I know that.

301
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,360
Okay, it's all right.

302
00:25:01,840 --> 00:25:03,840
Am I really getting old now?

303
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:12,040
Why are my parents no longer here?

304
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:47,200
GRACE UPON DESCENDANTS

305
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:50,400
IN MEMORY OF BELOVED MOTHER,
XU RUOSHU

306
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:02,680
Mom, you haven't met her yet.

307
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,160
This is Sang Zhi.

308
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:09,960
I've told you about her before.

309
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:12,280
Now,

310
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,440
she is my girlfriend.

311
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:21,720
Mom.

312
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:24,280
I might settle down in Nanwu later.

313
00:26:25,320 --> 00:26:26,400
But don't worry.

314
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:29,760
I'll come and visit you every year.

315
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,280
I came today mainly to tell you

316
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,640
that Dad has also passed away.

317
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:38,600
He passed away

318
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:41,560
quite peacefully.

319
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:45,120
Don't worry.

320
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,680
I fulfilled his wish

321
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:49,040
and found a serene place for him.

322
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:50,040
I wonder

323
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:52,680
if you two will meet over there.

324
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,880
If you do…

325
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,560
Never mind.

326
00:27:16,520 --> 00:27:18,920
As long as both of you
are happy and content.

327
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:52,720
Hello, Mrs. Duan.

328
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,720
I'm Sang Zhi.

329
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,480
You don't have to worry.

330
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,760
Duan Jiaxu is now

331
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:06,360
a very kind and outstanding person.

332
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:11,360
He treats people well

333
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,600
and is very sincere.

334
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:14,720
He excelled in his studies

335
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,360
and performs well at work.

336
00:28:17,120 --> 00:28:18,280
To me,

337
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,520
my parents,

338
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,320
and everyone,

339
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:24,920
he is a wonderful person.

340
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,880
Although some bad things

341
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:32,720
had happened in the past,

342
00:28:33,320 --> 00:28:35,480
he never gave up on himself.

343
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,720
Instead, he worked hard

344
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:40,360
and endured everything

345
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:43,800
with a lot of hardship.

346
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,000
If only

347
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:51,360
you could see how excellent he is now.

348
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:53,640
I'm sure you would have some regrets

349
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:56,200
and worries too, right?

350
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:59,600
But don't worry.

351
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,680
I'll take good care of him.

352
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,640
I'll make it up to him.

353
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:08,240
I'll make sure

354
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:10,840
he is happy every day.

355
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,560
So I'll also give you my promise.

356
00:29:17,040 --> 00:29:18,600
As long as I am here,

357
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:22,760
I won't let anyone bully Duan Jiaxu again.

358
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:36,240
He'll have his own family in the future.

359
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,680
He has me

360
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,520
and many others who love him.

361
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,120
We all love you.

362
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:55,000
So

363
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:59,280
you will never be alone anymore.

364
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:02,160
Okay?

365
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,560
Don't cry.

366
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:08,880
If you cry,

367
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:12,640
your mom will think I'm bullying you.

368
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:14,920
The smoke is stinging my eyes.

369
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,200
You promised.

370
00:30:19,320 --> 00:30:21,000
You promised in front of my mom

371
00:30:21,080 --> 00:30:23,160
that you'll protect me.

372
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,760
Yes, I'll protect you.

373
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,920
Come here.

374
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,320
Let me protect you for a bit.

375
00:30:41,760 --> 00:30:43,200
Hey.

376
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,080
Come and get me.

377
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:01,720
Come after me.

378
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,160
I can even stand up.

379
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,960
That little girl

380
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:10,920
who used to sit in my back seat

381
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,680
suddenly grew up one day.

382
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:16,240
She can always accompany me

383
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,360
and walk side by side with me.

384
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:21,040
She helped me overcome

385
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:23,080
my longest and darkest hour.

386
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,720
She even took the lead

387
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:28,040
and waited for me

388
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,160
in the sunlight.

389
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,040
Come on!

390
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:39,960
I'm coming!

391
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,680
I've submitted my resignation to Siyun.

392
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:23,400
Why?

393
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:28,440
Didn't I tell you before?

394
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:30,080
You don't have to go back to Nanwu.

395
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,760
I want to go back.

396
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:33,960
I want

397
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:36,160
to go in advance and get things settled.

398
00:32:37,040 --> 00:32:38,680
When you graduate and return to Nanwu,

399
00:32:38,760 --> 00:32:40,240
you can immediately start a good life.

400
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:43,160
Besides, your family is there.

401
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,960
I can start my business anywhere, right?

402
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:48,680
My home is where you are.

403
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:53,480
Didn't you say

404
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:56,200
that after all the bad things are over,

405
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:59,360
all that is left are the good things?

406
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:03,080
So we just need to focus on the future.

407
00:33:04,280 --> 00:33:05,760
Our future.

408
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,280
Okay?

409
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,800
How long will it be before leaving?

410
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:19,040
After completing the handover procedures,

411
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:20,760
about a month later.

412
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,440
A month?

413
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:27,920
That's so soon.

414
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,480
Are you feeling reluctant?

415
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:35,640
No.

416
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:40,160
But I feel reluctant.

417
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:50,840
Don't worry.

418
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,600
We'll have many opportunities to meet up.

419
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:11,320
I'm making supper for you.

420
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,239
Supper?

421
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,639
Glutinous rice balls.

422
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,199
How about six?

423
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:18,800
Is that okay?

424
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:54,199
Okay, that's enough.

425
00:34:56,159 --> 00:34:57,680
That's too much water.

426
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,200
Really?

427
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,160
Let me do it.

428
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,760
That's about it.

429
00:35:22,120 --> 00:35:23,800
I'm going to miss you after I leave.

430
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,840
What am I going to do?

431
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:34,920
If you miss me,

432
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:37,840
you can eat the candy I gave you.

433
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:39,120
Okay?

434
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:41,400
Or you can bring the polar bear with you.

435
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:45,520
What will you do if you miss me?

436
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,320
I'll leave the polar bear with you.

437
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,560
If you miss me,

438
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:55,800
you can look at it.

439
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,640
It will be just like I'm right beside you.

440
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,080
Okay?

441
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,560
It's not done yet.

442
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:15,320
Do you want…

443
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,640
What are you thinking about?

444
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,640
Why don't you go and get some rest?

445
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:26,840
I'll be done soon.

446
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,200
How about…

447
00:37:27,200 --> 00:37:28,120
All right.

448
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,240
I've called a car for you.

449
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:32,960
Text me after you get in the car.

450
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,600
The airport is so far.

451
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,720
I shouldn't have let you see me off.

452
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:42,000
How could I not come to see you off?

453
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,480
I don't want you to leave.

454
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:00,760
I know.

455
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,680
Don't worry.

456
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,120
After I get there,

457
00:38:07,040 --> 00:38:08,520
I'll visit you whenever I have time.

458
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,000
I won't make you wait too long. Okay?

459
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,040
Listen.

460
00:38:17,560 --> 00:38:19,520
Once you're back in Nanwu,

461
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,840
you need to eat regularly.

462
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:23,760
You must have

463
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,560
three meals a day.

464
00:38:26,640 --> 00:38:27,840
But I'll remind you.

465
00:38:28,920 --> 00:38:29,960
And also,

466
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:32,280
don't think

467
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:34,160
about other things.

468
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:35,400
Don't be concerned about them.

469
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:37,560
Just focus on your work

470
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:39,200
and work hard.

471
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:40,600
You can work hard,

472
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,680
but don't stress yourself too much.

473
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,480
I mean,

474
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:47,800
if your start-up does fail,

475
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,040
it's okay.

476
00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:51,840
After all, I can…

477
00:38:53,640 --> 00:38:54,520
You can what?

478
00:38:56,240 --> 00:38:57,360
I'll provide for you.

479
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,960
After I graduate, I can provide for you.

480
00:39:03,080 --> 00:39:04,520
You always say you'll provide for me.

481
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,320
Then I'll just wait.

482
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,160
All right.

483
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:13,760
Well,

484
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,560
I'm going to go now.

485
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:17,720
Don't stay any longer.

486
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:19,720
Okay?

487
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,680
Text me after you get in the car.

488
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,360
I'm going now.

489
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:39,000
Be good.

490
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:42,960
Text me when you get in the car.

491
00:39:43,040 --> 00:39:43,880
Head back now.

492
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,000
Bye.

493
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,480
Let me send you off.

494
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,480
Okay.

495
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,720
Then send me off.

496
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,640
This is far enough.

497
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,600
I really have to go now.

498
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:54,240
Head back now.

499
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,760
Text me when you get in the car.

500
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,760
Make sure to text me.

501
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:41,560
What is it?

502
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:43,960
I have a feeling

503
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:46,320
that you have something to tell me.

504
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:51,760
After you go to Nanwu,

505
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:54,800
can we have video calls every day?

506
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,440
Of course we can.

507
00:41:57,400 --> 00:42:00,240
You won't find it burdensome, will you?

508
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:02,680
Will you find it burdensome?

509
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:04,720
-No.
-Me neither.

510
00:42:08,920 --> 00:42:09,840
You try it first.

511
00:42:12,480 --> 00:42:13,360
Okay.

512
00:42:25,600 --> 00:42:26,480
One more thing.

513
00:42:28,040 --> 00:42:30,600
We'll be in a long-distance relationship,

514
00:42:31,200 --> 00:42:32,120
so we should

515
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:34,600
make an extra effort.

516
00:42:34,680 --> 00:42:38,720
For example, on anniversaries or holidays,

517
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,080
I can visit you in Nanwu

518
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:41,920
or you can visit me in Yihe.

519
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,080
Of course.

520
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:44,920
Then I shall go and visit you.

521
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,960
Hold on. What do you mean by that?

522
00:42:48,040 --> 00:42:49,280
Are you saying

523
00:42:49,360 --> 00:42:50,800
that I usually don't make an effort?

524
00:42:51,600 --> 00:42:52,480
That's not it.

525
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:54,560
So do you agree with it?

526
00:42:54,640 --> 00:42:55,800
Of course.

527
00:42:55,880 --> 00:42:56,720
Good.

528
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:06,720
And also,

529
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:10,280
if we have an argument…

530
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:12,480
We won't argue.

531
00:43:13,440 --> 00:43:15,080
But if we do,

532
00:43:15,160 --> 00:43:16,840
we must make up on the same day.

533
00:43:17,640 --> 00:43:19,280
No silent treatment. No disappearing.

534
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:22,360
-Got it?
-We make up on the same day we quarrel.

535
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:24,480
Well said.

536
00:43:27,200 --> 00:43:28,440
Trust.

537
00:43:29,080 --> 00:43:31,160
We trust each other.

538
00:43:31,240 --> 00:43:32,160
Actually…

539
00:43:32,760 --> 00:43:33,800
If…

540
00:43:34,800 --> 00:43:36,960
-What are you reading?
-Wait. No.

541
00:43:38,520 --> 00:43:40,720
"Guide to maintaining
a long-distance relationship"?

542
00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:42,760
As you know,

543
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:44,600
many problems come up

544
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:46,800
in long-distance relationships.

545
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:48,880
So I summarized them in advance

546
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:52,520
and developed a guide.

547
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:55,400
So you don't trust me

548
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:56,560
and are worried about me.

549
00:43:57,760 --> 00:43:59,000
No.

550
00:44:00,800 --> 00:44:02,120
I'm pretty worried about you.

551
00:44:02,680 --> 00:44:04,120
I think your guide

552
00:44:04,200 --> 00:44:05,720
is done very well.

553
00:44:05,800 --> 00:44:07,080
You should strictly follow it

554
00:44:07,160 --> 00:44:08,000
in the future.

555
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:09,840
Me?

556
00:44:11,440 --> 00:44:12,520
Quickly send me a copy.

557
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:17,120
You can make your own.

558
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:18,960
I'm serious.

559
00:44:19,040 --> 00:44:20,600
What you wrote is really good.

560
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:28,200
Wait.

561
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:31,040
"We can have arguments,

562
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:33,200
but not in front of other people."

563
00:44:33,280 --> 00:44:34,720
Yes, because it's a matter

564
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:36,200
of saving our face.

565
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:40,560
"You don't have to reply
to messages instantly.

566
00:44:40,640 --> 00:44:42,200
But if you see them, you must reply."

567
00:44:42,280 --> 00:44:44,200
-That's right.
-If you see them, you must reply.

568
00:44:44,280 --> 00:44:47,320
Yes, you have to reply if you see it.
Got it?
